{"tid":202811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一篇新聞就睇得出香港人同大陸人本質無異","createTime":"2017-04-15T18:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T19:01:36.000Z","uid":4804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5794bbcc3f2a2787fef7e783723a41292679d9c","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:52:09.000Z","msg":"復活節公眾假期進入第二日，早上10時半已經有大量市民在中環5號碼頭「打蛇餅」排隊等坐船入長洲過節。有市民指，原本打算前往台灣短途旅行，但旅行團早已爆滿，惟有改為到長洲玩；亦有人專程帶同由澳洲遠道而來的朋友前往長洲遊覽，不認為會為當地居民帶來不便，「我哋入去玩係帶旺長洲。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然前往長洲的慢船向來較少人選搭，但今日卻全船滿座，甚至有乘客要企足全程。市民李生和太太原本打算到台灣玩，可惜旅行團皆爆滿，只能留港消費，「未諗玩咩，入去睇吓嘢先啦。」<br />\n<br />\n黃先生陪同澳洲朋友到長洲玩，問及為何選擇在假期人多「趁墟」，他指上年已來過，「排隊都唔會排好耐啫，我估10幾分鐘，好快過」，對於有長洲人不滿每逢假日遊人太多影響他們生活，黃先生反指遊客有助長洲發展，「我哋帶旺長洲呀！」<br />\n<br />\n年輕情侶胡先生和唐小姐稱原本無打算到長洲，「前一刻先決定咋」，由於臨時起意，二人都無計劃旅程，「去到再睇玩咩」，胡先生更打趣說，「同佢（唐小姐）一齊去邊都開心。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0B00xJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0B00xJJ.jpg&h=09853b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡先生與女友臨時起意入長洲郊遊。（張志華攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要不是我們，長洲早就完蛋了<br />\n咁講究竟同大陸人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5089f12d1102fe9e29c0f0b36b5d9d8f6d36d30e","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:55:08.000Z","msg":"無人回就挑戰10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcabd210b2b54c63aad9886d1563342acbec453","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:55:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fe9938bd19507cc6627773b6b29ae5f1a6c3e923","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d8a819ad682241720bd61799fb9adc3de266cfca","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:56:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3c4219cf26ad201eef40eb55eadaa02950075fc8","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:57:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f65b3035026ec17dcbf7638e534a84b2f51d7d49","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:57:44.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"1ef709eef914bdff1229bbe35e17f90c20cdd0ef","tid":202811,"uid":15897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72fe57cea62988ecb1adb67ca042f4634a7eb5b","tid":202811,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:57:49.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"b78d2ff227d468c1f662096b3bfae42f73d24e69","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"再黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1"},{"pid":"0ff24cc4c94fa7daa1ee98ca1399f9c14e66dcfc","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:59:50.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ce2dfb87405454cdc3a719d7f136bb4fb4b52bf3","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:00:23.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9d777b9be662e22d1199da64188539d3688fbf4e","tid":202811,"uid":4804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:01:08.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"b8a14121eb1835a90ca4d20449b3e40fdc68558a","tid":202811,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:01:36.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係嫁啦<br />\n出到外國鬼死咁失禮人"}]}